| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2815 — Recovery Inhibition (blacknevas)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 388cb3a2-e1c2-5a01-954f-b7ddf91f1404"
